			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">NCA precursor refers to a precursor compound used in the production of lithium nickel cobalt aluminum oxide (LiNiCoAlO2), which is a cathode material for lithium-ion batteries. This precursor is processed to a specified level of purity, ensuring compliance with quality standards. It includes important information on the method of production and the starting materials used. The description also indicates if the product is supplied as part of a production or consumption mix and specifies the point in the supply chain where it is available, such as 'to consumer' or 'at plant'.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">NCA前体指的是用于生产锂离子电池正极材料——锂镍钴铝氧化物（LiNiCoAlO2）的前体化合物。这种前体经特定纯度等级处理，确保符合质量标准。它包括生产方法和使用的起始材料的重要信息。描述还表明产品是作为生产或消费混合物之一供应的，并指出供应链中的可用点，如'给消费者'或'在工厂'。</common:generalComment>
